{"tid":202394,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日三餐 15/04/2017","createTime":"2017-04-15T12:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T14:58:32.000Z","uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce7df47171e80617b368c772c3f7ad54efc345f6","tid":202394,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:46:32.000Z","msg":"胃潰瘍好得7788 終於有番啲胃口食野<br />\n本身已經瘦底 依家病完得番100磅鬆啲<br />\n想試下係度記錄低自己每日食過既野<br />\n順便提醒自己每日要食多啲<br />\n<br />\n今日同屋企人跟團番大陸 順德兩日一夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n#早餐<br />\n腿蛋治 熱檸茶<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/15/203817_d97d1d0dca67e8795a86cbf5b853b163.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F15%2F203817_d97d1d0dca67e8795a86cbf5b853b163.jpg&h=33e9a1c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/15/203847_14550dfd338cdfa89fc90fcbed1b4a9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F15%2F203847_14550dfd338cdfa89fc90fcbed1b4a9a.jpg&h=a685943f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n9點鐘黎到深圳灣等集合<br />\n依度啲早餐好撚貴 30蚊個三文治<br />\n係貪佢有得坐住等唔洗係出面企<br />\n<br />\n#午餐 #自助韓燒火鍋<br />\n白飯 雞髀 淥少少肉同菜 煎蛋 兩隻餃子<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/15/203920_25a2b1a89b779f7887192384830c802b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F15%2F203920_25a2b1a89b779f7887192384830c802b.jpg&h=f0067179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為左個胃著想 啲油膩野一舊都冇食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n#晚餐 #屌又係韓燒加火鍋<br />\n冇野啱食 食左啲米粉同菜 少少肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/15/203959_d907065c91b6d792e7a150bae70a6433.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F15%